bio: Just a regular guy who loves crypto.
impactDescription: I'm always posting positive content on Twitter as well as my DeBank stream when it comes to OP.  I am a big supporter of Velodrome on OP as well as Aerodrome now on Base.  I've also been active in discord asking/answering questions.  Thank you for all you do for OP.
contributionDescription: My contribution would be more geared toward education and awareness.  I do most of this just speaking to my friends and family face to face, but I have also tweeted and have used my DeBank stream to raise awareness.  I don't have a ton of followers but I am a big supporter of Velodrome on OP.
